roductivity and decision-making accuracy.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5d00b6d all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5d00b6d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-8\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">The Future of CRM: What\u2019s Next for Einstein in 2025 and Beyond<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a6cc41a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a6cc41a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salesforce Einstein is evolving fast. With GPT integrations, natural language prompt engines, and cross-cloud intelligence on the way, the future of Salesforce AI focuses on proactive and conversational CRM. Soon, instead of just viewing data, businesses will be able to interact with it in real time.<\/span><\/p><p><b>Forward-thinking companies are already preparing by:<\/b><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reviewing their CRM data readiness<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Testing GPT-powered automation for marketing and sales<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Planning multi-channel AI workflows for better customer experiences<\/span><\/li><\/ul><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now is the right time to invest in Einstein, because as AI-powered CRM continues to advance, businesses that act early